title: Rex Mundi - Explore Heaven E.P. (2013) (320kbps) (AciDToX8)
description:
Rex Mundi - Explore Heaven E.P.                                     

                              Trance | Armind (Armada)

             320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-09-09 | 00:25:17 | 59 Mb


No Mundi record leaves the studio without the quality seal of rocking steady. Keeping his standards high, it's now brought him his Armind debut. The 3 track 'Explore Heaven' E.P. shows the many talents of the Dutch producer - knowing how to rock you is one of many. Shortly after his 'Hidden Treasures' E.P., Rex Mundi's got another three lined up for your dance floor approval. We reckon he'll get it. 'Cause whether you love the proggy depths of 'Aureolo', the ethnic drums of 'Voodoo People' or the warm, piano melody of 'Explore Heaven', there's more than enough going on in this E.P. to blow your mind.
